## Ignore build outputs
**/bin/
**/obj/

## Ignore git artifacts
.git/
.gitignore
.gitattributes

## Ignore IDE/editor files
.vs/
.vscode/
*.user
*.suo
*.sln.DotSettings

## Ignore test results and coverage
**/TestResults/
coverage/

## Ignore logs
logs/
*.log

## Ignore Docker files from context (except the one being used)
**/Dockerfile*
**/.dockerignore

## Ignore docs and scripts not needed at runtime
README.md
docs/
*.sh
*.ps1
